{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:1","prev_osis_id":"Isa.057.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le vrai je\u00fbne<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. \u00c9s 1:10-20. (Mt 6:16-18. Jon 3:5-10.) (Mi 6:8. Mt 3:8.) (\u00c9s 56:2-7. J\u00e9 17:19, etc.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Crie \u00e0 plein gosier, ne te retiens pas,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\u00c9l\u00e8ve ta voix comme une trompette,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et annonce \u00e0 mon peuple ses iniquit\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A la maison de Jacob ses p\u00e9ch\u00e9s!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.57.21","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 57:21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.57.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:2","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Tous les jours ils me cherchent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils veulent conna\u00eetre mes voies;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme une nation qui aurait pratiqu\u00e9 la justice<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et n\u2019aurait pas abandonn\u00e9 la loi de son Dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils me demandent des arr\u00eats de justice,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils d\u00e9sirent l\u2019approche de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:3","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Que nous sert de je\u00fbner, si tu ne le vois pas?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">De mortifier notre \u00e2me, si tu n\u2019y as point \u00e9gard?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, le jour de votre je\u00fbne, vous vous livrez \u00e0 vos penchants,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vous traitez durement tous vos mercenaires.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:4","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Voici, vous je\u00fbnez pour disputer et vous quereller,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour frapper m\u00e9chamment du poing;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous ne je\u00fbnez pas comme le veut ce jour,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour que votre voix soit entendue en haut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:5","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\n    Est-ce l\u00e0 le je\u00fbne auquel je prends plaisir,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Un jour o\u00f9 l\u2019homme humilie son \u00e2me?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Courber la t\u00eate comme un jonc,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et se coucher sur le sac et la cendre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Est-ce l\u00e0 ce que tu appelleras un je\u00fbne,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Un jour agr\u00e9able \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:6","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Voici le je\u00fbne auquel je prends plaisir:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">D\u00e9tache les cha\u00eenes de la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">D\u00e9noue les liens de la servitude,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Renvoie libres les opprim\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que l\u2019on rompe toute esp\u00e8ce de joug;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:7","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    Partage ton pain avec celui qui a faim,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et fais entrer dans ta maison les malheureux sans asile;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si tu vois un homme nu, couvre-le,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ne te d\u00e9tourne pas de ton semblable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:8","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Alors ta lumi\u00e8re poindra comme l\u2019aurore,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ta gu\u00e9rison germera promptement;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ta justice marchera devant toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la gloire de l\u2019\u00c9ternel t\u2019accompagnera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:9","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alors tu appelleras, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel r\u00e9pondra;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu crieras, et il dira: Me voici!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si tu \u00e9loignes du milieu de toi le joug,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les gestes mena\u00e7ants et les discours injurieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:10","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Si tu donnes ta propre subsistance \u00e0 celui qui a faim,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si tu rassasies l\u2019\u00e2me indigente,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ta lumi\u00e8re se l\u00e8vera sur l\u2019obscurit\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tes t\u00e9n\u00e8bres seront comme le midi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:11","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel sera toujours ton guide,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il rassasiera ton \u00e2me dans les lieux arides,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il redonnera de la vigueur \u00e0 tes membres;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu seras comme un jardin arros\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme une source dont les eaux ne tarissent pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:12","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Les tiens reb\u00e2tiront sur d\u2019anciennes ruines,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu rel\u00e8veras des fondements antiques;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">On t\u2019appellera r\u00e9parateur des br\u00e8ches,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui restaure les chemins, qui rend le pays habitable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:13","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.058.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Si tu retiens ton pied pendant le sabbat,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour ne pas faire ta volont\u00e9 en mon saint jour,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si tu fais du sabbat tes d\u00e9lices,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour sanctifier l\u2019\u00c9ternel en le glorifiant,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et si tu l\u2019honores en ne suivant point tes voies,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">En ne te livrant pas \u00e0 tes penchants et \u00e0 de vains discours,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:14","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.58.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Alors tu mettras ton plaisir en l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je te ferai monter sur les hauteurs du pays,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je te ferai jouir de l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de Jacob, ton p\u00e8re;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car la bouche de l\u2019\u00c9ternel a parl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.58","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc4437fc0.56594959');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc4437fc0.56594959\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc4437fc0.56594959","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc4437fc0.56594959'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc4437fc0.56594959\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}